Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收手吧 兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你意欲何為 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:02:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道兄長你的性慾乃大陸首屈一指
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然放著眼前的妹妹不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將魔手伸向嘉依卡 實在是不能坐視不理呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槽點太多我都不知從哪吐起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我聲明我是清白的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您太謙虛了 兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無防備睡在一旁的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對兄長你來說 不就如同擺在猛獸眼前的生肉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我當成什麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奇伊啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還記得啊 值得誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神秘人物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何貴幹? 又帶來了什麼新情報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了下一位英雄的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙·斯坎尼亞 科尼柯賽克王國的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後確認其行蹤是在四年前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離這三日車程的 拉德米歐市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四年前?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少能當作個追尋他的線索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其實打從一開始就全都知道吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遺體的位置啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 至少我是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不過是一名使者罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得是上了你的套 令人很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 那挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡情地懷疑 苦惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正希望你們如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不歸谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走過路過不要錯過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這有南方礦山挖出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最高純度的魔法思念料喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法思念料 品種齊全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個要 這個也買
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不歸谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本就是個經常佈滿濃霧的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可自從四年前起 一點也不放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入谷者沒人再出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是出了棄獸啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就不得而知了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟就連去確認的人們 也都沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知都還是死是活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失蹤? 西蒙·斯坎尼亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這男人原來是軍中的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.72,0:04:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但戰爭結束後 馬上就失去了蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 沒想到被稱作英雄的男人竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前些日子的阿巴爾特伯爵也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認已經病死的多明妮卡·斯考達也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為輝煌的八英雄的下場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人不免感到詫異啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至還有傳聞 說這是賈茲皇帝的詛咒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詛咒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼活了五百年 能使用怪物般的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟那是個有著各種詭異傳說的人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳聞先不說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但賈茲皇帝的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是從金錢的角度 或是作為高純度的魔法思念料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是無以倫比的絕品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此說不定得到它 會導致人們喪失正常的判斷力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:04:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若嘉依卡一行人打算接觸西蒙·斯坎尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就應該會在這拉德米歐市現身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會繼續調查的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正馭使小梟進行探查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才想確認下 他有沒有在聚精會神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也別用針刺他頭來試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薇薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「針」對你來說 就如同對我來說的「劍」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不應該輕易拔出鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器能救人 也能傷人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要慎重選擇使用之處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到那隊嘉依卡·賈茲及亂破師了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪兒?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在城市另一頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙·斯坎尼亞 住所不歸谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 正好和他消失的時期相一致
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有這個可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 準備機杖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持隨時能發動的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 離這麼遠也能感知到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面應該還有魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想做無益的爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白日做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡·賈茲 我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收集賈茲皇帝的遺體 到底有什麼企圖?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親 祭悼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭悼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說 你的目的就僅僅如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能輕信她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這肯定是她為了逃走而隨口編的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 嘉依卡能拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去做掉基烈特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:06:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒什麼勝算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰意已決嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就全力以赴 一決雌雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士 亞伯力克·基烈特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此對汝等宣戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼情況?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在做什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是廝殺?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯真不公平!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算我一份啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝鎧龍?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她們同伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是我情願如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想跑呢 幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒~? 那廝殺呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不想我死在其他人之手吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝鎧龍居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了 再晚一點就危險了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法思念料 全部遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再買不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢? 回機車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那幫傢伙還在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不方便接近城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往北邊飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越過森林應該有個濃霧山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Efun Heluste Ru NBelguil Fai Sev
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯現吧 探測者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Locator
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探測魔法 無效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能…那也是魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法? 那霧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理論上 可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 龐大力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力源 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遺體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性 有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之不能貿然下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想從空中觀察一下情況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能載著我們 去山谷上方轉一圈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不幹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為托魯你言而無信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也是 明明說好幫你就和我打的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒說不和你打啊 總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天是幾時?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天? 明天?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天就是總有一天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長 不管管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你想幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遺體 這下面 探索
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣應該沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長 怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我還能怎麼辦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又做了那個時候的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到現在我仍偶爾會想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時從懸崖上摔下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許活下來的不該是我 而是阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 不要責備自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能走到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆因一直有托魯在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我世上最重要的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說也是 若我沒遇到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也過不上這樣充實的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因有你在我身邊 我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感激你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼情況?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理解 不能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然應儘早處理掉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 請求 冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 在這
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詳情 不明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一可能性 魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影 精神支配 多重效果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯的妄想 成形顯現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}等等我啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神影響 霧所變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}等等~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯笨蛋 笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個嘉依卡 以及建築 全都是霧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…既然會見到那種幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說兄長心中有那樣的願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下流無恥 必須立即喚醒兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 解除結界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去救兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險 恐怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 阿卡莉 芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「守護者」魔法效果範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除 立即 與霧接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到精神支配 與托魯同樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是不能吸到霧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能在這眼睜睜看著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方法 只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 到這邊來 良機到來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法解除 托魯捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法再度 起動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這旅途也接近尾聲了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 只剩下一件遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打敗亞伯力克·基烈特搶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有困難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是也只有上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不用再收集遺體了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來接你了 嘉依卡!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞伯力克!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞伯力克?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要與亞伯力克結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈? 結婚?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 那收集遺體呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為只要和亞伯力克在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的遺體自然就能到手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 我好高興!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我祭悼完父親 我們就舉辦婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可你不是說要和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為一國的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然是要挑選個門當戶對的對象才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎可能一直和個低賤亂破師混在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 至今多謝你啦托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後會無期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就此別過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 請等等 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要拋棄我嗎~~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 往這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 解除結界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要丟下我獨自一人~~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡~~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦啦 醒醒!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來一切都是幻覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摔下來時 只有托魯沒能回收到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 接下來該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一到結界外 就又幻覺叢生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本無法移動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移動 可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干涉魔法 霧中擊入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方魔法 部分妨害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擊入魔法的那一部分 就可以自由行走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法發動 移動 反復
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 然後再破壞掉對方的機杖就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊 那個魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是出於什麼目的才施加了這種魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到本人直接問他就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若他還活著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,統率者 顯現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:17:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,統率者 顯現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eim Halmus Rom
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Naint milta ru
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利刃呀奔流吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Ripper
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來魔法解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙·斯坎尼亞在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒禮貌 擅自闖入別人家中…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是西蒙·斯坎尼亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壞掉了 真是不中用的廢鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底魔法這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關鍵時刻就連個屁用都頂不上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是西蒙·斯坎尼亞吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西蒙? 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是什麼西蒙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得八英雄中有這個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然變化很大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再回軍隊 絕不回…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部隊位置被敵人知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差點就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差點就死了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除我之外 大家全死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是馬魯克那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那傢伙把部隊出賣給了敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那混蛋 還擺出一副好友的嘴臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是馬魯克的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 馬魯克那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是在講戰爭時的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還把艾蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的至愛妻子奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個那個都是叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都給我去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遭到了同伴和妻子的背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是離開軍隊 獨自住在了這樣的山谷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 剛才的魔法是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怪就怪被騙的人自己傻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭泣 絕望 然後全都化為白骨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是想讓人看到被信任之人背叛的幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓別人也遭受和他同樣的經歷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我剛才那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遺體 返還 希望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 女兒 賈茲的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賈茲 女兒…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親祭悼 遺體 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遺體?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 那正可謂這世上最無用的破爛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要就趕緊拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們拿走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼? 捨不得?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要 那種東西我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 若要回拉德米歐市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能爬上這崖壁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.31,0:21:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明被稱作英雄 還得到了財產和遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下場卻這麼悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我想那麼多也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 善良
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這倒不是因為善良…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻覺 我與托魯兩人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個嘛 別太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 背叛 不會 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.34,0:21:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,講起來 那怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎會和嘉依卡那樣…對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒謬了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過畢竟阿卡莉和芙蕾多妮卡是絕對不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也許只好選了嘉依卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長 為什麼我是絕對不可能?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 想想就知道了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…你好像生氣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.87,0:22:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛中!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山嶺的帝國?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樸實的人們 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 大家 故鄉一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我 祖國記憶 基本沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周 第八集 「暫慰的帝國」
